.I val compare 
: 
.B t -> t -> int
.sp
The comparison function for 64\-bit integers, with the same specification as
.B Pervasives\&.compare
\&.  Along with the type 
.B t
, this function 
.B compare
allows the module 
.B Int64
to be passed as argument to the functors
.B Set\&.Make
and 
.B Map\&.Make
\&.
.sp

